        {
            "id": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/02/16/programe/PHP-MySQL/",
            "url": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/02/16/programe/PHP-MySQL/",
            "title": "PHP-MySQL",
            "date_published": "2022-02-16T11:32:33.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"php-连接mysql\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#php-连接mysql\">#</a> PHP 连接 MySQL</h1>\n<h2 id=\"一-mysqli-面向对象\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#一-mysqli-面向对象\">#</a> 一： MySQLi- 面向对象</h2>\n<h3 id=\"11-使用前基本配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#11-使用前基本配置\">#</a> 1.1 使用前基本配置</h3>\n<p><strong>在 php.ini 中开启 mysqli 扩展</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight ini\"><figcaption data-lang=\"ini\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token key attr-name\">extension</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">php_mysqli.dll</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>重启服务器</p>\n<p>然后，创建数据库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><figcaption data-lang=\"SQL\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">database</span> mysqli<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">table</span> news<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>    id <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">auto_increment</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">primary</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">key</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">comment</span> <span class=\"token identifier\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span>主键<span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>    title <span class=\"token keyword\">varchar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">not</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">null</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">comment</span> <span class=\"token identifier\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span>标题<span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>    content <span class=\"token keyword\">text</span> <span class=\"token operator\">not</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">null</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">comment</span> <span class=\"token identifier\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span>内容<span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token keyword\">engine</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token keyword\">Innodb</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">charset</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>utf8 <span class=\"token keyword\">comment</span> <span class=\"token identifier\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span>新闻表<span class=\"token punctuation\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">// 插入数据</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">insert</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">into</span> news <span class=\"token keyword\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'sanguo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'caocao'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>unix_timestamp<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">insert</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">into</span> news <span class=\"token keyword\">values</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'shuihu'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'luzhishen'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>unix_timestamp<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id=\"12-连接数据库\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#12-连接数据库\">#</a> 1.2 连接数据库</h3>\n<p>连接代码如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><figcaption data-lang=\"PHP\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$servername</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"localhost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 主机</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$username</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"username\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 用户名</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$password</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"password\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 密码</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$dataname</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"data\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">// 数据库</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysqli_connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$servername</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token variable\">$username</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token variable\">$password</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token variable\">$dataname</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token keyword\">die</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"连接失败:\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_connect_err</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_set_charset</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'urf8'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token delimiter important\">?&gt;</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>解析：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><figcaption data-lang=\"PHP\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">/*</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>mysqli_connect (主机地址，用户，密码，数据库名，端口号); 如果端口号 默认是 3306 可以不写</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>连接成功会返回一个资源，不成功会返回一个 bool 值</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>mysqli_connect_error () ; 返回错误信息</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>mysqli_connect_errno (); 返回错误编码</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>mysqli_set_charset (数据库资源变量，编码)； // 设置数据库名 数据库资源变量就是连接成功后获得的变量，后面是 字符编码</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>*/</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id=\"13-数据操作语句\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#13-数据操作语句\">#</a> 1.3 数据操作语句</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>通过 mysqli_query (数据库资源，sql 语句) 执行查询语句</li>\n<li>增，删，改语句执行成功返回 true，失败返回 false</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><figcaption data-lang=\"PHP\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token variable\">$con</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysqli_connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'localhost'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'root'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'mima'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'data'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token keyword\">die</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"连接失败：\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_connect_error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token keyword\">exit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$res</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysqli_query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"insert into news values(null,'sanguo','caocao',unix_timestamp());\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$res</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"插入成功&lt;br/&gt;\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">// 执行 SQL 语句</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">// 执行 insert 语句 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"insert into news values (null,'静夜思','床 前明月光',unix_timestamp())\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"15\"></td><td><pre>    \t<span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'自动增长的编号是：'</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_insert_id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 获取最近一次插入记录的 id 值</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"16\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">// 执行 update 语句 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"17\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$link</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"update news set content='疑是地上霜' where id=4\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"18\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"19\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'受影响的记录数是：'</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_affected_rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 返回最近一次 增删改的影响的行数</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"20\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"21\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 数据查询用 select、desc、show，成功会返回结果集，失败返回 false </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"22\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'错误码：'</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_errno</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$link</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'&lt;br&gt;'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"23\"></td><td><pre>        <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'错误信息：'</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$link</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"24\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"25\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">// 查询数据</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"26\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysqli_query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'select * from news'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"27\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token function\">var_dump</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 输出 $rs 的类别  结果：  object (mysqli_result)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"28\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 获取对象中的数据</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"29\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 将对象中的一条数据匹配成索引数组，指针下移一条</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"30\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$rows</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysqli_fetch_row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"31\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 将对象中的一条数据集匹配成关联数组，指针下移一条</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"32\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$rows</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_fetch_assoc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"33\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 将对象中的一条数据匹配成索引，关联数据，指针下移一条</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"34\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$rows</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysqli_fetch_array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"35\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'总行数'</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_num_rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"36\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'总列数'</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">mysqli_num_fields</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"37\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 获取所有数据</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"38\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token variable\">$list</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">mysqli_fetch_all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 默认是索引数组</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"39\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token function\">mysqli_free_result</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 销毁结果集</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"40\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 关闭连接</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"41\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token function\">mysqli_close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$con</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 获取最近一次执行增，删，改，影响的记录数</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"42\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token delimiter important\">?&gt;</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"二-pdo\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#二-pdo\">#</a> 二： PDO</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PDO (PHP Data Object) 扩展为 PHP 访问各种数据库提供了一个轻量级，一致性的接口。无论访问什么数据库，都可以通过一致性的接口去操作</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"21-基本配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#21-基本配置\">#</a> 2.1 基本配置</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight ini\"><figcaption data-lang=\"ini\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token key attr-name\">extension</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">php_pdo_mysql.dll</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id=\"22-pdo核心类\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#22-pdo核心类\">#</a> 2.2  pdo 核心类</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>PDO 类，表示 PHP 和数据库之间的一个连接</li>\n<li>PDOStatement 类\n<ol>\n<li>第一： 表示执行数据查询语句 (select ,show) 后相关结果集</li>\n<li>第二： 预处理对象</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n",
            "tags": [
                "MySQL"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/01/15/MySQL/mysql%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/",
            "url": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/01/15/MySQL/mysql%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/",
            "title": "mysql数据库笔记",
            "date_published": "2022-01-15T01:32:33.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>创建数据库<br>\n create database sis2107;</p>\n<p>删除数据库<br>\n drop database sis2107;</p>\n<p>创建表，并添加约束<br>\n create table table (id int auto_increment primary key,user varchar (4) not null,password varchar (10),sex char (4));<br>\n 注：添加条件必须设置主键</p>\n<p>添加表，不设置主键<br>\n create table table1 (id int,user varchar (4),password varchar (10),sex char (4));</p>\n<p>修改表，添加主键<br>\n alter table table1 add primary key (id);</p>\n<p>添加表，添加唯一主键<br>\n create table table2 (id int primary key,user varchar (4),password varchar (10),sex char (4));</p>\n<pre><code> create table table3(id int,user varchar(4),password varchar(10),sex char(4),primary key(id));\n</code></pre>\n<p>添加表，添加复合主键<br>\n create table table4 (id int,user varchar (4),password varchar (10),sex char (4),age int (11),primary key (id,age));</p>\n<p>添加表，添加唯一约束<br>\n create table table5 (id int,user varchar (4),password varchar (10),sex char (4),age int (11),unique (id));</p>\n<p>查看表中约束<br>\n show create table table2;</p>\n<p>修改表<br>\n alter table table1 rename tables1</p>\n<p>添加字段<br>\n ALTER TABLE table1 ADD age int default null;</p>\n<p>删除表<br>\n drop table table1；</p>\n<p>删除字段<br>\n alter table table1 drop name;</p>\n<p>添加数据<br>\n insert into table1 values (1,\"xiaoqiao\",18,\"woman\",\"2002\");</p>\n<pre><code>insert into table1(id,name,age,sex,birthday) values(1,\"xiaoqiao\",18,\"woman\",\"2002\");\n\ninsert into table1(id,name,age,sex,birthday) values(1,\"xiaoqiao\",18,\"woman\",\"2002\"),(1,\"xiaoqiao\",18,\"woman\",\"2002\");\n</code></pre>\n<p>删除数据<br>\n delete from table1 where id=1;</p>\n<pre><code>delete from table1\n</code></pre>\n<p>修改数据<br>\n update table1 set name=\"fff\",sex=\"man\",age=22 where id=2;</p>\n<pre><code>update table1 set name=\"aaa\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>查询数据<br>\n select * from table1;</p>\n<pre><code>select id,name from table1;\n</code></pre>\n<p>按条件查询<br>\n select * from table1 where id&lt;6;</p>\n<p>按条件查询 “in”，查询集合<br>\n select * from table1 where age in (56,22);</p>\n<p>按条件查询 “BETWEEN AND”，查询范围<br>\n select * from table1 where id between 1 and 5;</p>\n<p>空值查询<br>\n select * from table1 where id is null;</p>\n<pre><code>select * from table1 where id is not null;\n</code></pre>\n<p>按条件查询 “DISTINCT”，去重数据<br>\n select distinct sex from table1;</p>\n<p>LIKE 模糊查询<br>\n “%” 通配符查询  查询指定范围 \"w% n/% n/w%\"<br>\nselect * from table1 where sex like \"w%n\";</p>\n<pre><code>“_”下划线查询   查询缺少字符\"m_n/w__an\"\n\tselect * from table1 where sex like \"m_n\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>and 条件查询<br>\n select * from table1 where id&gt;5 and sex=\"man\";</p>\n<p>or 条件查询<br>\n select  * from table1 where id&lt;5 or age&gt;30;</p>\n<p>and,or 一起查询<br>\n select * from table1 where id&lt;5 or sex=\"man\" and age&lt;50;</p>\n<p>聚合函数<br>\n count ()  返回字段条数<br>\n select count (*) from table1;</p>\n<pre><code>sum()    返回数值和\n\tselect sum(age) from table1;\n\navg()   返回平均值\n\tselect avg(age) from table1;\n\nmax()   返回最大值\n\tselect max(age) from table1;\n\nmin()   返回最小值\n\tselect min(age) from table1;\n</code></pre>\n<p>order by   排序查询<br>\n select * from table1 order by age;         正序<br>\n select * from table1 order by age desc;    倒序</p>\n<p>group by   关键字分组查询<br>\n单独使用<br>\n select * from table1 group by sex;</p>\n<pre><code>和聚合函数一起使用\n\tSELECT COUNT(*) ,age FROM table1 GROUP BY age;\n\nGROUP BY 和 HAVING 关键字一起使用\n\tSELECT sum(age),sex FROM table1 GROUP BY sex HAVING SUM(age) &lt; 300;\n</code></pre>\n<p>limit 限制查询结果数量<br>\n select * from table1 limit 4;</p>\n<pre><code>select * from table1 limit 4,7;\n</code></pre>\n<p>取别名 AS<br>\n 表取别名（当即返回，不是永久）<br>\nselect * from table1 as t where t.name=\"ccc\";</p>\n<pre><code>列取别名（当即返回，不是永久）\n\tselect name as user from table1;\n</code></pre>\n<p>子查询 (嵌套查询)<br>\nselect * from table1 where id&lt;(select age from table1 where name=\"ccc\");</p>\n<p>联合查询<br>\n select version () union select user ();</p>\n<p>内置表查询<br>\n查询数据库：<br>\nselect schema_name from information_schema.schemata;</p>\n<pre><code>查询表名：\n\tselect table_name from information_schema.tables;\n\n查询列名：\n\tselect column_name from information_schema.columns;\n\n查询数据：\n\tselect * from students;\n</code></pre>\n",
            "tags": [
                "MySQL"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/01/15/MySQL/MySQL%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/",
            "url": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/01/15/MySQL/MySQL%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/",
            "title": "MySQL基础语法",
            "date_published": "2022-01-15T01:32:33.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"基本简介\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#基本简介\">#</a> 基本简介</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Sql 语句的学习主要为渗透中关于 Sql 注入漏洞打下坚实基础</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"1-数据库操作\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1-数据库操作\">#</a> 1. 数据库操作</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>基本的数据库操作，包括数据库连接，数据库基本语法</p>\n<p>SQL 是用于访问和处理数据库标准的计算机语言</p>\n<p>SQL 指结构化查询语言，全称是 Structured Query Language</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"11-数据库连接\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#11-数据库连接\">#</a> 1.1 数据库连接</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>输入命令  <code>mysql -uroot -p</code>   之后回车是密文连接</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/image-20220115100526170.png\" alt=\"image-20220115100526170\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>​\t输入命令  <code>mysql -uroot -p密码</code>  回车 则是明文连接</p>\n<ul>\n<li><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/image-20220115100928878.png\" alt=\"image-20220115100928878\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"12-退出\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#12-退出\">#</a> 1.2 退出</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Exit</li>\n<li>quit</li>\n<li>\\q</li>\n<li>ctrl+c</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"13-常用的sql语句\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#13-常用的sql语句\">#</a> 1.3 常用的 SQL 语句</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><figcaption data-lang=\"SQL\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> version<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 查询当前数据库版本</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 查询当前数据库用户</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> @<span class=\"token variable\">@basedir</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 查询当前路径</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">databases</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 查询所有数据库</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> databasename<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># databasename 为数据库名</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>shou <span class=\"token keyword\">tables</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 查询所有表名</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">database</span> 数据库名 <span class=\"token comment\"># 创建一个数据库</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">desc</span> 表名<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 查询表结构</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">drop</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">database</span> 数据库名<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 删除一个数据库</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"14-sql-dml-和-ddl\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#14-sql-dml-和-ddl\">#</a> 1.4 SQL DML 和 DDL</h2>\n<p>SQL 语句可以分为两部分： 数据操作语言 (DML) 和 数据定义语言（DDL）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"sql-的-dml-部分\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#sql-的-dml-部分\">#</a> SQL 的 <mark>DML</mark> 部分</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><mark>SELECT</mark> - 从数据库表中获取数据</li>\n<li><mark>UPDATE</mark> - 更新数据库表中的数据</li>\n<li><mark>DELETE</mark> - 从数据库中删除数据</li>\n<li><mark>INSERT INTO</mark> - 向数据库表中插入数据</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"sql-的-ddl\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#sql-的-ddl\">#</a> SQL 的 <mark>DDL</mark></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><mark>CREATE DATABASE</mark>  - 创建数据库</li>\n<li><mark>ALTER DATABASE</mark> - 修改数据库</li>\n<li><mark>CREATE TABLE</mark> - 修改数据库表</li>\n<li><mark>DROPTABLE</mark> - 删除表</li>\n<li><mark>CREATE INDEX</mark>- 船舰索引</li>\n<li><mark>DROP INDEX</mark> - 删除索引</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>注意：</strong>  <mark>SQL 对大小写不敏感</mark></p>\n<h2 id=\"15-sql中的-tips\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#15-sql中的-tips\">#</a> 1.5 SQL 中的 tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>符号运用</p>\n<ul>\n<li>=====   \t\t数据库的赋值符号</li>\n<li><mark>or/||</mark>     逻辑或</li>\n<li><mark>xor</mark>      逻辑异或</li>\n<li><mark>&amp;&amp;/and</mark>       逻辑与</li>\n<li><mark>NOT/！</mark>  逻辑非</li>\n<li><mark>+ - * /</mark>  基本运算符</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>常用注释符</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h1 id=\"\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#\">#</a> </h1>\n</li>\n<li><mark>--</mark> + 空格</li>\n<li><mark>/**/</mark></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"2-数据库常用函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2-数据库常用函数\">#</a> 2. 数据库常用函数</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>有关数据库基本函数的功能介绍和基本用法</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"21-updatexml-语法updatexml目标xml文档xml路径更新的内容\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#21-updatexml-语法updatexml目标xml文档xml路径更新的内容\">#</a> 2.1   <code>updatexml()</code>   语法 updatexml (目标 xml 文档，xml 路径，更新的内容)</h2>\n<p>语法： <code>select updatexml('anything',concat('~',(select version())),'xxx');</code></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/image-20220115141947255.png\" alt=\"image-20220115141947255\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"22-substring函数leftmid函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#22-substring函数leftmid函数\">#</a> 2.2  <code>substring()</code>  函数， <code>left()</code> , <code>mid()</code>  函数</h2>\n<p>语句：  <code>select substring(user(),1,2);</code></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/image-20220115142319448.png\" alt=\"image-20220115142319448\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"23-ifabc-如果a为真则返回b否则返回c\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#23-ifabc-如果a为真则返回b否则返回c\">#</a> 2.3  <code>if(a,b,c)</code>  如果 a 为真，则返回 b，否则返回 c</h2>\n<p>语句：  <code>select if(length(database())=5,1,0);</code></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/image-20220115142721804.png\" alt=\"图2-3\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"24-hex-unhex-函数\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#24-hex-unhex-函数\">#</a> 2.4  <code>hex() &amp;&amp; unhex()</code>  函数</h2>\n<p>渗透中有些注入点因为数据库中对数据字段的类型定义，可能不支持<mark> union</mark> 来显示某些不同类型的内容，所以使用<mark> hex</mark> 对数据进行 16 进制的编码</p>\n<p><code>hex()</code>  参数可以是任何类型</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sql\"><figcaption data-lang=\"SQL\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>slect hex<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>concat<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>selec hex<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> hex<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">database</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/image-20220115144258184.png\" alt=\"结果\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"3-mysql-数据库基本数据类型\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#3-mysql-数据库基本数据类型\">#</a> 3. MySQL 数据库基本数据类型</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>介绍 MySQL 数据库的基本数据类型</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"31-数值类型\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#31-数值类型\">#</a> 3.1 数值类型</h2>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/1624934729617-62cc7f2f-4fa9-417a-9e0d-286841d9db06.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>注意</strong> 数据库中回经常涉及到关于金额的存取，涉及到金钱的存取应当采取 <mark>MEDIUMINT</mark> 这种大整数值</p>\n<h2 id=\"32-日期和时间类型\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#32-日期和时间类型\">#</a> 3.2 日期和时间类型</h2>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/1624934749713-cf3fa5ec-36f6-4b34-a011-2760b12394c9.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"字符串\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#字符串\">#</a> 字符串</h2>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/1624934764195-2399cd03-1085-434a-b7fc-e3f61a45bc75.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n",
